title: 141. Q&AF: Sharks & Spoons
itunes:title: 141. Q&AF: Sharks & Spoons
description: Some things aren't for everyone. On today's Q&AF episode, Andy talks about how reading books has improved his life drastically and how it can do the same for you, when you should take that next big step in growing your business, and how to overcome complacency when working towards your goals.
